Kita mo talaga sa ceatsg na walang accountability e, nagturn off comments, nagdelete pa ng comments, walang public statement/apology pati masyadong reply sa mga concerns. Andami ninyong taong na-agrabyado tapos wala lang? 
Kaya mas maraming natuwa sa cbaasg bukod sa business students sila at alam nila how to handle big events like this, they know how to handle critism. Nabash din naman yung flaire last time pero after ng concert puro thank you cbaasg na yung mga comments. Sa ceat puro padin problema yung comments pano imbis na iaddress tinurn off comments o kaya dinelete. Hindi naman magiging possible ung event nyo kung walang attendees, kailangan nyo pa din kami kung gusto nyo maging successful yung solfest nyo.
Accept criticism and be accountable kung gusto nyong magkaroon nang marami pang solfest kung pinagpapatuloy nyo nyan for sure maraming madadala at hindi na aattend kahit maganda pa pasabog at line up nyo.
Daming reklamo about solfest, yes may late updates sila pero ewan if na-immune kaming mga unattend sa flair na last minute yung guidelines na binaba.
